Jason Faunt https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jason_Faunt 0 Jason Patrick Faunt (born November 20, 1974, in Chicago, Illinois) is an American actor who is best known for the role as Wesley Collins in Power Rangers Time Force, as well as that of Alex, the former Red Time Force Ranger. Faunt grew up in the Chicago suburb of McHenry, Illinois. He attended McHenry High School East Campus. Due to his athletic prowess in high school, he used a partial baseball scholarship to attend the University of North Carolina at Asheville, where he earned a business degree. He originally was going to become a Major League Baseball player after graduating, but moved to Los Angeles instead to pursue an acting career. Faunt has two children with his Ex-wife Stephanie.He is set to appear in the upcoming film The Order alongside other Power Rangers alumni.
